data.description: Welcome to this beautiful home located in Tollgate Village.  Wonderfully low maintanced front yard with large back yard and a covered patio.  Walk into this beautiful home with gorgeous hardwood floors throughout the main level, stairs and hall. You can tell the home has been loved and well taken care of with many upgrades to include upgraded vinyl windows.  The beautiful formal living room and dining room greet you as walk in the front door.  The home has a lovely kitchen, new stainless steel applicances, with a nice eating space leading out  to a covered patio and large yard.  The kitchen and eating space flow into the family which has a cozy wood burning fireplace, perfect for cold nights.  Large windows view the backyard and patio. A remodeled half bath is located on the main floor also.  The 2nd floor of the home has a large primary owner ensuite with remodeled bathroom and large closet.  A hallway remodeled bath and 2 nice bedrooms complete the second floor.  The basement has a nice non-conforming bedroom with full bathroom.  Around the corner is large finished recreation room perfect for entertaining.  A large laundry  and mechanical room complete the basement.  Please note there is an assumable VA loan at an interest rate of 2.75.
